                  <div>
                    <label class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase mb-1 block">Project Details</label>
                    <textarea class="w-full bg-slate-950 border border-slate-700 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg p-2.5 h-24 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-500 outline-none resize-none placeholder-slate-600" placeholder="Briefly describe your current system (e.g. Rockwell PLCs, Ignition 8.1) and what you need to achieve..."></textarea>
                  </div>

